            <title>[CASSANDRA-12720] Permissions on aggregate functions are not removed on drop</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-12720</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a user defined aggregate is dropped, either directly or when it&apos;s enclosing keyspace is dropped, permissions granted on it are not cleaned up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
